]]></Comment><ReturnType>DWORD</ReturnType><ReturnBitSize>32</ReturnBitSize><Parameter><Name>RecipeManager</Name><Type Namespace="Recipe_Management">IRecipeManager</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize></Parameter><Properties><Property><Name>conditionalshow</Name><Value>visu_coredev</Value></Property></Properties></Method><Method><Name>GetLastError</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Returns the last error of the previous operation

