 :return: See :ref:`ReturnValues` for a description of all possible errors.]]></Comment><ReturnType Namespace="Recipe_Management">InfoValues</ReturnType><ReturnBitSize>32</ReturnBitSize></Method><Method><Name>prvCompareRecipe</Name><ReturnType>BOOL</ReturnType><ReturnBitSize>8</ReturnBitSize><Parameter><Name>RecipeDefinitionName</Name><Comment><![CDATA[	Name of the recipe definition ]]></Comment><Type ReferenceTo="true">STRING(80)</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>InOut</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Parameter><Name>RecipeName</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Name of the recipe ]]></Comment><Type ReferenceTo="true">STRING(80)</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>InOut</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Local><Name>recSel</Name><Type Namespace="Recipe_Management">IRecipeSelection</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>recSelCompare</Name><Type Namespace="Recipe_Management">IRecipeSelectionWithCompare</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize></Local></Method><Method><Name>ReloadRecipes</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Reloads the list of recipes from the file system

